      • register

        void register(String key,
              FieldFactory factory)
        Registers a field factory for use in the config.
        Parameters:
        key - a globally unique string for use in the config to identify this field. Valid chars are A-Z, a-z, 0-9, underscore. hyphen
        factory - the factory to register
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if the key contains invalid characters
        IllegalStateException - if the key has already been registered
